{"tid":329112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺中國人/香港人社會縱鳩壞哂D細佬","createTime":"2017-07-20T05:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T09:56:32.000Z","uid":187,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3bec0f17f86cc3083eb12f08b0b9fd144726bdf","tid":329112,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:57:42.000Z","msg":"坐車又想人讓 7-8歲仲好力過你我啦仆街<br />\n有時我都唔撚明d死廢老帶細路出街有位會比左個細路先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次見有人讓撚完比佢地 都唔會坐定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇戲又嘈<br />\n搭飛機又嘈<br />\n踩到人/撞到人D家長都唔會覺得有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講句唔好意思係唔係咁難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n永遠都係有人話細路哥係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係香港人唔撚識教呀你老母"},{"pid":"0a796afa28d890082a5a8760b80a2b5492e012dc","tid":329112,"uid":82436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"上到小四就長大啦，啊占"},{"pid":"53b5652add8125a2bcceb42fd6a416328908fd4f","tid":329112,"uid":109567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"我諗起以前<br />\n係中西區室內場打完波行緊出去 望下d細路打羽毛球 突然有個望左我一陣之後話：你望乜野？望夠未？<br />\n屌你老尾10歲都未夠串77 仲要有大人係格黎 好心d垃圾唔撚教仔就唔好生啦"},{"pid":"9a8e4c00d20dfa479963024b15d0471275af43fe","tid":329112,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"中國人的細佬被寵壞新係正常事。一子政策，係主要原因。"},{"pid":"60def7fd15a888a524f5714789164bd5f0467a36","tid":329112,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"啲細路細細個就好聽話,又靜守規矩大個咪又係變毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係呢啲就係毒撚嘅幼年體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327c453b72fa255dfc1a1c45bd7a29e1d6b3af6b","tid":329112,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy